次进行过现场劝导和清理。 工作人员表示，馆藏的文物大部分都位于封闭展示柜中，但部分非文物的场景或模型属于开放展区。随意投掷的这些钱币和杂物，既影响展示功能，也会给其他观众造成误导，而且清理起来还十分困难。往展区投币，不管出于什么目的，都属于一种不文明的观展行为。 马竹松表示，这个造型场景暂时无法密封，但是后期会在这里做更多的警示，提醒观众关注不要再往里投币。观众向“茅草棚”撒钱？！云南省博物馆回应…"},"attached_info":"Cj8I4PTR//30/qQWEAMaCDc0NDQwMTIxIMrYxY0GMB04qgNAJ3IJNTA0NzE1MjgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed67097c6626daf59be18d62151b34c8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1639314937.6771975","card_id":"Q_504341210","target":{"id":504341210,"title":"有哪些能让人原地大破防的句子？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/504341210","type":"question","created":1638866260,"answer_count":132,"follower_count":504,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[17884,37795,410903],"comment_count":8,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I4PTR//30/qQWEAMaCDc0MzU2ODcxINS6vI0GMAg4+ANAKHIJNTA0MzQxMjEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-771f135afb526738431afa859a36712d_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"41_1639314937.677573","card_id":"Q_325071577","target":{"id":325071577,"title":"你见过的最喜欢的表情包是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/325071577","type":"question","created":1558242148,"answer_count":266,"follower_count":1844,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24632,29713,164890,164962],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I4PTR//30/qQWEAMaCDM0NTEzODQ2IOTGg+cFMAQ4tA5AKXIJMzI1MDcxNTc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer",